VinSolutions announced today its Customer Relations Management software has been approved as a Infiniti Certified Lead Provider.  

As a result, Infiniti dealerships using MotoSnap are able to seamlessly receive electronic leads directly from Nissan. Advantages of utilizing a Certified CRM provider means the dealership can receive electronic leads from Nissan directly, eliminating other processes and allowing for quicker responses, while reducing errors or attrition of data.  The integration with VinSolutions enhances this integration by ensuring automatic daily prospecting and sales follow-up processes.